- You were going to behave.

1127
01:18:34,146 --> 01:18:38,424
I don't know how you do this. People
drive me crazy. It won't happen again.

1128
01:18:38,586 --> 01:18:42,419
- Where was I?
- Don't sweat the small stuff.

1129
01:18:42,585 --> 01:18:45,657
